-- Rostelecom May Pay $510 Million in Dividends, Kommersant Says
-- B y   S t e p h e n   B i e r m a n
-- 2012-04-24T03:50:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-24/rostelecom-may-pay-510-million-in-dividends-kommersant-says.html
OAO Rostelecom management will
propose paying 14.96 billion rubles ($510 million), or 32.48
percent of 2011 net income, in dividends,  Kommersant  said,
citing an unidentified person close to the company board of
directors.  The proposal of 4.69 rubles a share will be heard at an
April 27 board meeting, Kommersant said, citing the same person.  To contact the reporter on this story:
